## Data Model

### Silver Layer (BigQuery)

**price_5min_avg** — 5-minute windowed average price per flight
```
flight_number, route_id, origin, destination, airline_code, airline_name,
window_start, window_end, avg_price_usd, min_price_usd, max_price_usd,
message_count, processing_timestamp
```

**price_1hr_trend** — 1-hour sliding window average per flight
```
flight_number, route_id, origin, destination, airline_code,
window_start, window_end, avg_price_usd, message_count, processing_timestamp
```

**late_arrivals** — messages arriving >2 minutes after event time
```
route_id, flight_number, origin, destination, airline_code, price_usd,
flight_date, event_timestamp, ingestion_timestamp, lateness_seconds,
processing_timestamp
```

### Gold Layer (BigQuery)

**Grain:** One row in `fact_flight_prices` = one flight × one 5-minute window

**fact_flight_prices**
```
flight_key (FK), airline_key (FK), date_key (FK),
window_start, window_end,
avg_price_usd, min_price_usd, max_price_usd, message_count,
is_anomaly, z_score, created_at
```

**dim_flights (SCD Type 2)**
```
flight_key (surrogate), flight_number (natural),
route_id, origin, destination, airline_code,
effective_date, expiry_date, is_current
```

**dim_airlines**
```
airline_key, airline_code, airline_name, alliance, is_domestic
```

**dim_date**
```
date_key, date, day_of_week, day_number,
is_weekend, month, quarter, is_us_holiday, season
```

